## Installation
```bash
pip install myprofiler
```

## Usage
```python
from myprofiler import profile

@profile
def main():
    lt = []
    for i in range(0, 100000):
        lt.append(i)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
```
output:
```bash 
========================================
---- Meta Data ----
Function: main
Method: None
---- Memory Usage ----
Current memory usage:	 936.0B
Peak memory usage:	 3.4MiB
---- Time ----
Total Time:	 0:00:00.039728
seconds:	 0
microseconds:	 39728
========================================
```
